{
  "stem": "14613.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Later on, when they started the aussiedlungs, then, of course, they came in, too.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But even that was done mostly by the Jewish police.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that-- every now and then, we would have some big-shot Germans come in to our resort and inspecting the merchandise, inspecting what we are doing.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we did not have such a direct contact.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, they would go sometimes, if they are going and somebody was in their way, they would beat them up or do things like this.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But by and large, it was minimal.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Surely if you had people that were smuggling food or other things from ghetto or to ghetto, if they were caught, then they had problem with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But this, again, was incidence-- it was not the widespread situation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, there were-- it is, like I said, it's an amazing thing that even under the most trying circumstances, I would say the spirit-- call it the Jewish spirit, or the spirit of man-- somehow could still flourish.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you had people like Bajgelman, who was directing the-- the symphony concert in Lodz.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He-- he was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] not only conducting the-- the orchestra, but he was also composing music.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that this played an important part in giving us the-- the will to live.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That even under the most trying circumstances, you could have the-- the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the intellectual life that existed [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] before the war, and you could have it still in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Under what conditions was the music performed?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where and how?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The music were really particular, like they're all performed in a big rooms and halls.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was not heated.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
